{"tid":1144862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"批涂謹申做大龍鳳 霸住逃犯條例主席 黃毓民串爆： 係咪同美國佬交差？","createTime":"2019-05-08T10:18:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T13:56:49.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"101709dbdb448c905b6ff2638d5c8981c84afb33","tid":1144862,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:18:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkgpao.com/articles/1001936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgpao.com%2Farticles%2F1001936&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2Fcn%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=d1f136dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkgpao.com/articles/1001936</a><br />\n<br />\n批涂謹申做大龍鳳<br />\n霸住逃犯條例主席<br />\n黃毓民串爆：<br />\n係咪同美國佬交差？<br />\n2019.05.08 14:00 時事<br />\n<br />\n反對派涉集體非法開逃犯條例「會議」，宛如小學雞玩「煮飯仔」。算半個同路人、時時被指是內鬼的「癲狗」黃毓民都忍不住發炮，指反對派以為自己開到會好威，然而他們的「會議」根本不合法，更質疑涂謹申搞出大龍鳳，強行霸主席之位，「係咪同美國佬交差」？<br />\n<br />\n黃毓民日前在網台節目評論反對派兒戲非法開會，不齒於反對派針對立法會秘書處，因為秘書處是跟規矩做，如沒有他們堅守規則，反對派只會「死得仲快」。黃又警告愚蠢的反對派，指他們再不按照秘書處的指引開會，到時只有建制派出席合法會議，屆時可任意通過住何條款。<br />\n<br />\n不齒反對派針對秘書處<br />\n黃毓民更突破盲腸，質疑涂謹申「係咪同美國佬交差」、係咪同「某啲人」交差？顯然是質疑涂謹申的連串行動背後有甚他目的。<br />\n<br />\n黃色同路人鬧起泛民起來，真係講得特別入肉。你覺得黃毓民咁樣串爆涂謹申同泛民，係咪好有道理？"},{"pid":"1f378aa463cb6cbd3e3028198e57178b6456e822","tid":1144862,"uid":41458,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:18:55.000Z","msg":"邊撚個係黃毓民?<br />\n呢條友仲有人識嫁咩"},{"pid":"ff10fa51a86215cbdb36d581fd91316fcd22ff10","tid":1144862,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1f378aa463cb6cbd3e3028198e57178b6456e822","tid":1144862,"uid":41458,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:18:55.000Z","msg":"邊撚個係黃毓民?<br />\n呢條友仲有人識嫁咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:19:25.000Z","msg":"抄登仔之前捧個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb87afd36e406bc674a7af9f6fd5e15173d8eb27","tid":1144862,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:21:55.000Z","msg":"何為邪鬼何為神"},{"pid":"f04a968ba584e941dd7af743cfd654424cb853c9","tid":1144862,"uid":193436,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:22:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bfe9acf7705f2e68fa84c7de642b132c37a6c810","tid":1144862,"uid":7699,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"1f378aa463cb6cbd3e3028198e57178b6456e822","tid":1144862,"uid":41458,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:18:55.000Z","msg":"邊撚個係黃毓民?<br />\n呢條友仲有人識嫁咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:29:26.000Z","msg":"因選輸左俾個𡃁妹而聲言退出政壇、個仔因藏毒喺大陸被捕嘅黃毓民"},{"pid":"778c31ccec1c1b5c70f9672156d941813458ad06","tid":1144862,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70c8807d2faf7fb0749bd13f2959a777e06c4a3","tid":1144862,"uid":85629,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:46:11.000Z","msg":"有人同大陸交差？"},{"pid":"92f8db4961ef136edfee5a63c0b6b44da6fccd2a","tid":1144862,"uid":402,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bfe9acf7705f2e68fa84c7de642b132c37a6c810","tid":1144862,"uid":7699,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"1f378aa463cb6cbd3e3028198e57178b6456e822","tid":1144862,"uid":41458,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:18:55.000Z","msg":"邊撚個係黃毓民?<br />\n呢條友仲有人識嫁咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:29:26.000Z","msg":"因選輸左俾個𡃁妹而聲言退出政壇、個仔因藏毒喺大陸被捕嘅黃毓民"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:48:09.000Z","msg":"因民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2520027dc3402cea674b4ae0a9a56e3dc89fd31","tid":1144862,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db60a068563ae4bffe14aac781c6e7bad33b15c","tid":1144862,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re